msgid "The main objective of this working group is to consolidate, enhance, and modernize Quarkus's Ahead-of-Time (AOT) and runtime efficiency (in JVM mode) capabilities. We aim to leverage OpenJDK's Project Leyden, IBM Semeru's advanced features, and JLink to provide a unified, \"native-like\" startup exper\n"
